  "response": "As of recent trends, many startups across various industries in Kolkata are actively seeking freshers to join their teams. Some notable startups that might be hiring include:\n\n1. **CareStack**: Dental practice management.\n2. **WOW! Momo**: Food & Beverage.\n3. **iMerit**: Data enrichment and AI services.\n4. **Sasta Sundar**: Healthcare and pharmacy.\n5. **Xenium Digital**: Digital marketing and advertising.\n6. **Trell**: Social commerce and lifestyle community platform.\n7. **Techshu**: Digital marketing.\n8. **SkyQuest Technology Consulting Pvt. Ltd.**: Market research and consulting.\n9. **EazyCoach**: Education technology.\n\nTo get the most accurate and up-to-date information, it\u2019s recommended to visit specific job portals such as LinkedIn, Naukri.com, Indeed, or Freshersworld. Additionally, joining local startup communities and attending tech meetups in Kolkata can give insights into which startups are currently hiring.",
